[*] --> Draft
Draft --> Completed : update
Completed --> Processing : review
Completed : entry / log message
Processing --> Approved : process
Processing : entry / log message
Approved --> Delivered : reject
Approved : entry / log message
Delivered --> Reviewed : process
Delivered : entry / log message
Reviewed --> [*]
